ributions from the slow neutron-capture process and the rapid\nneutron-capture process. Instead, we argue that this anomalous signature can be\nexplained by assuming an additional contribution by the intermediate\nneutron-capture process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 5 Nov 2014 21:21:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
