od can be folded-unfolded a significant\nnumber of times without loosing its characteristics, a phenomenon that is\nbelieved to be important for the bacterium to keep close contact to the host\ntissue and consequently helps the bacterium to colonize the host tissue.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 6 Nov 2014 13:13:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-07"}
